Source: linux-odroid
Section: kernel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Dongjin Kim <tobetter@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 8.0.0)
Standards-Version: 4.8
Homepage: http://github.com/tobetter/linux

#
# Upstream Linux kernel release
#
Package: linux-image-odroid-upstream
Architecture: armhf arm64
Depends:
	linux-image-5.4.0-odroid-upstream-armmp [armhf],
	linux-image-5.4.0-odroid-upstream-arm64 [arm64],
Description: Upstream Linux kernel and modules
 The Linux kernel and modules for Hardkernel's SBC ODROID based on
 ARMv7/8 platforms.

Package: linux-headers-odroid-upstream
Architecture: armhf arm64
Depends:
	linux-headers-5.4.0-odroid-upstream-armhf [armhf],
	linux-headers-5.4.0-odroid-upstream-arm64 [arm64]
Description: All header files for upstream Linux kernel
 This package provides the architecutre-specific kernel header files for
 Hardkernel's SBC ODROID based on ARMv7/8 platforms.

